Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was a cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A cliff?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a height that we could jump from.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sister wasn't lying,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the demons didn't underestimate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With that cliff,\Nsecurity wouldn't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.08,0:01:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that means we can't escape from the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.58,0:01:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.46,0:01:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there is a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I tried going to the edge of the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It split into two more walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One side continued along the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The other wall was the side of our House.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The angles were about 60 degrees each.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.73,0:02:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The inside of the two walls,\Nwhere it splits, were nearly symmetrical.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the same scenery in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.61,0:02:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It means this Grace Field House is on\Na hexagonal property surrounded by a cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the lot west from our Plant Three\Nis probably the headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That lot was the only one with a bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we're surrounded by cliffs, then crossing\Nthe bridge will be the only way to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom is calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Tell her that I'll be right there.\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.23,0:03:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give this back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.45,0:03:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you were planning to return\Nfrom the start, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You said so yourself, right?\NThat we'll stay alive together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you were already planning to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Sorry, I lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't afford to make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I can't let anyone die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I run away, the plan will deviate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it deviates even a little,\Nit'll be problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even want a chance of losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless to argue.\NI won't change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I did what I can today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure the escape succe—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.16,0:03:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Norman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because of you two, I had a good life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.47,0:04:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Norman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's still not too late to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Run and hide in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like I just said,\NI'm not going to change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've caught a cold again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No more snowball fights, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can't play with Norman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not until he gets better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So listen everyone,\Ndon't enter the infirmary for a while, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E-Emma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I came to visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why? You can't come in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Norman, you always feel lonely\Nevery time you get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want you to feel sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk so you don't have to, so let's hang out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, we can't. You'll catch my cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was told that I don't get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.08,0:06:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Emma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When did you sneak in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do if you got sick, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Ray said I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ray?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This book said idiots don't get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you can't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go near the infirmary anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, Emma?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Emma, you can't...\N- Here, this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:06:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ray taught me how to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.14,0:07:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you really don't give up, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He said we can talk by using these!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hello?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Norman, can you hear me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, I can hear you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Now we can talk\Neven though I'm out here! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you yell like that,\Nyou don't even need the string phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Let's go, Norman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.21,0:08:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Don't get sick, okay?\N- Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sherry, please don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of a crying face,\Nsend me off with a smile, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norman...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can I count on you to help Emma in my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma, where's Ray?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.53,0:08:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He said he didn't want to see Norman off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don. Gilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Emma and Ray, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course. Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:08:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of everyone, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.23,0:09:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- See you later!\N- Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Norman!\N- Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.79,0:09:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll distract Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:10:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! I know you're reckless,\Nbut this is too far, Emma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't what you should be doing right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I won't let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not wishing for any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you to send me off with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please understand how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. I just can't respect those feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Especially if you don't even want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're crazy, Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reckless and unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Naïve and immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.82,0:10:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's time, Norman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that you're sad,\Nbut you're getting too hotheaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you cause another commotion, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, is it all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if I say my last goodbye to Emma?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.53,0:11:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for tricking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get anymore injuries, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And don't be reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eat properly, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay. Don't ever give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your suitcase is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because no matter what I put in,\NI can't take it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't have ever ran away.\NI knew it from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's praiseworthy. You're doing the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can ship out Ray and Emma\Nwhen they're mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Until the end of the time that was decided,\Nhappily inside home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Spending a happy lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.18,0:13:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,are you happy, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was able to meet someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you wait in this room for a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, my dear children.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Remembering to appreciate that all 37 of you\Nare able to live here happily...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:14:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That one flew up high! Super high!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma looks so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen her look like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.52,0:15:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.77,0:15:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ray, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's been really depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}They both must be lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Well, the three of them were good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you want to talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have to decide what to do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From this point on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:16:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible. We're surrounded by a cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the only bridge going out\Nis in the headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.15,0:16:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to run away, then run.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dropping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ray, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Don. Gilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I did knock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're in pain. You're suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norman is dead, and Ray's a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do anything on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must be extremely despaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you will never be able to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The best way to not suffer from despair\Nis to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You suffer because you resist.\NSimply concede.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll feel much better. It's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you desire it, I'd like to recommend you\Nas the candidate to be Mom of this farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A candidate to be a Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Become an adult, have a child,\Nand if they approve your abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you can come back to this House\Nas a Mom or Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have the qualifications for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you desire it,\NI'd be happy to recommend you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Who would become such a thing?"\NIs that what you thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But then, what can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do anything. You can't save anyone.\NYou can only curse death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A cycle of suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.62,0:18:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Live and strive to become a Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.83,0:18:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Accept the despair\Nand free yourself from the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. I can't do that, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Then you can writhe in agony\Nas you await your death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.47,0:18:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You all cannot escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Think about that as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's my last night,\Nso I'm saying goodbye to the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ray, it's your birthday tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, tonight's the last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, it's goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't actually given up, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma.
